data.description: Historic 3-bedroom corner lot home in the Huntington Heights neighborhood of Newport News. This residence captures the essence of the area with its beautiful architecture and tree-lined streets. Located near to downtown, the home offers a mix of residential charm and city convenience. The neighborhood boasts a diverse community and is near parks and schools.Enjoy the convenience of proximity to shopping with options like Patrick Henry Mall and City Center at Oyster Point. Within minutes of Newport News Shipbuilding and a short commute to Fort Eustis. The home features an enclosed porch for cozy winter evenings. In the summer, relish the quaint backyard with a stone patio, creating a perfect space for outdoor enjoyment. This property combines historic charm with modern amenities, making it an ideal place to call home.
